 a sub-committee that set standards for admission to membership of its SVR category.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s13\sl240\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs72\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0\ltrch\hich\lang1033\loch\lang1033 The Commission initially also referred the complaint against two other firms, Bandit Limited and Global Telematics SA (Pty) Ltd, but withdrew against them on 15 November 2005.}}}
